room_title: Escape room "The Ultimate Nightmare" by Mainely Escapes in Waterville
review: I’ve played every room they have to offer at this location and each one is awesome! Their newest room, The Ultimate Nightmare, was one of the most fun rooms I’ve played in a while. If you’re looking for something different to do, I highly suggest this place!

room_title: Escape room "The Ultimate Nightmare" by Mainely Escapes in Waterville
review: We had so much fun in the ultimate nightmare! Can't wait to do more escape rooms!
